---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="Terms of Service" description="Terms of Service for Tier One Run Club" />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-background min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <Header />

    <main class="flex-1">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12">
        <div class="mb-8">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary">Terms of Service</h1>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-primary/60">
            Last updated: January 30, 2026
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none dark:prose-invert">
          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary">
              1. Acceptance of Terms
            </h2>
            <p class="text-primary/80">
              By accessing or using Tier One Run Club ("TORC", "we", "us", or
              "our"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do
              not agree to these terms, please do not use our service.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary">
              2. Description of Service
            </h2>
            <p class="text-primary/80">
              TORC is a fitness analytics platform that helps runners track,
              analyze, and improve their performance. Our service includes:
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-primary/80">
              <li>
                Integration with fitness devices and platforms (including Intervals.icu)
              </li>
              <li>Activity data import and storage</li>
              <li>AI-powered training analysis and recommendations</li>
              <li>Performance metrics and insights</li>
              <li>Training plan management</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary">
              3. Account Registration
            </h2>
            <p class="text-primary/80">
              To use TORC, you must create an account. You agree to:
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-primary/80">
              <li>Provide accurate and complete registration information</li>
              <li>Maintain the security of your account credentials</li>
              <li>
                Notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account
              </li>
              <li>
                Accept responsibility for all activities that occur under your
                account
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4 text-primary/80">
              You must be at least 13 years old to use this service. If you are
              under 18, you represent that you have your parent or guardian's
              permission to use the service.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary">
              4. User Content and Data
            </h2>
            <p class="text-primary/80">
              You retain ownership of all fitness data and content you upload to
              TORC. By using our service, you grant us a limited license to:
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-primary/80">
              <li>Store and process your data to provide our services</li>
              <li>Analyze your activities to generate insights and recommendations</li>
              <li>
                Use anonymized, aggregated data to improve our service (individual
                users will not be identifiable)
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4 text-primary/80">
              You may export or delete your data at any time through your account
              settings.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary">
              5. Third-Party Integrations
            </h2>
            <p class="text-primary/80">
              TORC integrates with third-party services such as Intervals.icu.
              Your use of these integrations is subject to the respective
              third-party terms of service. We are not responsible for the
              availability, accuracy, or content of third-party services.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-primary/80">
              When you connect a third-party account, you authorize us to access
              your data from that service as necessary to provide our features.
              You may disconnect these integrations at any time.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary">
              6. Subscription and Payments
            </h2>
            <p class="text-primary/80">
              Some features of TORC may require a paid subscription. By
              subscribing, you agree to:
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-primary/80">
              <li>
                Pay all fees associated with your subscription plan
              </li>
              <li>
                Automatic renewal of your subscription unless cancelled before the
                renewal date
              </li>
              <li>
                Provide accurate billing information and keep it up to date
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4 text-primary/80">
              Refunds are handled on a case-by-case basis. Contact us if you have
              concerns about your subscription.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary">
              7. Acceptable Use
            </h2>
            <p class="text-primary/80">You agree not to:</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-primary/80">
              <li>
                Use the service for any unlawful purpose or in violation of any
                applicable laws
              </li>
              <li>
                Upload false, misleading, or fraudulent data
              </li>
              <li>
                Attempt to gain unauthorized access to the service or other users'
                accounts
              </li>
              <li>
                Interfere with or disrupt the service or servers
              </li>
              <li>
                Reverse engineer, decompile, or attempt to extract the source code
                of the service
              </li>
              <li>
                Use automated systems or software to extract data from the service
                (scraping)
              </li>
              <li>
                Resell or redistribute the service without our written consent
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary">
              8. AI-Generated Content
            </h2>
            <p class="text-primary/80">
              TORC uses artificial intelligence to provide training analysis,
              recommendations, and insights. You acknowledge that:
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-primary/80">
              <li>
                AI-generated content is provided for informational purposes only
                and should not replace professional medical or coaching advice
              </li>
              <li>
                We do not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or suitability of
                AI-generated recommendations
              </li>
              <li>
                You should consult with healthcare professionals before making
                significant changes to your training regimen, especially if you
                have health concerns
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary">
              9. Health and Safety Disclaimer
            </h2>
            <p class="text-primary/80">
              TORC is a fitness tracking and analysis tool, not a medical device
              or service. You acknowledge that:
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-primary/80">
              <li>
                You should consult with a physician before beginning any exercise
                program
              </li>
              <li>
                You are solely responsible for your own health and safety during
